{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"当大地猛烈地震动，"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"抛其重担，"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"人们说：“大地怎么啦？”"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"在那日，大地将报告它的消息。"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"因为你的主已启示了它；"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"在那日，人们将纷纷地离散，以便他们得见自己行为的报应。"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"行一个小蚂蚁重的善事者，将见其报酬；"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"作一个小蚂蚁重的恶事者，也将见其恶报。"}]}